WORK IN PROGRESS


## Run in Vagrant

    vagrant up trusty
    vagrant provision trusty

    # or

    vagrant up xenial
    vagrant provision xenial

## Run in Docker

    sudo docker build -t ansible/django .

    sudo docker run -p 80 -p 443 \
      -v `pwd`:/srv/ansible/ \
      -v `pwd`/log/:/srv/site/log/ \
      -e DEBUG='True' \
      --rm -it ansible/django /srv/ansible/run.sh


## Role dependencies

- django
  - supervisor
  - sites
    - base
      - ntp
      - timezone
      - unattended
      - users

- postgis
